high_descs: walk to the round table on your right
pick up a knife from the table
locate a potato on this same table
cut several slices into the potato
walk to the fridge to your right open the door
put the knife inside the fridge
go back to the table with the potato on it
pick up a potato slice
take the potato slice to the microwave located to your left
place the slice in the microwave and cook it
turn to your left and go to the counter with the coffee maker
place the cooked slice on end in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of potato in front of a coffee maker

high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the round, black table.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table.
Move to the right to the potato that is on the table.
Cut the potato into slices with the butter knife.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the butter knife inside, close the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the potato on the table.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the microwave across the room.
Open the microwave, place the potato inside, close the door and turn the microwave on, then remove the cooked potato from the microwave.
Turn to the left and go to the coffee pot.
Place the potato on the counter in front of the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of potato in front of a coffee pot.

high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room, turn right toward the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn right, walk a short distance, turn left towards the table.
Cut the potato in slices.
Turn right, walk towards the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the knife inside.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn towards the table on the right.
Pick up a potato slice on table.
Turn around, walk across the room to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave, place the potato slice in, set microwave to 5 seconds, take out the potato slice.
Turn left, walk straight towards the counter.
Place potato slice on the counter next to the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your right, then walk straight until you reach the table on your right and turn right so that you are facing the table.
Pick up the knife on the table, that is between the spoon and the pepper.
Turn towards the black chair to your right and move forward slightly so that you are in standing beside the black chair.
Cut the potato on the table, that is between the plate and the pump bottle, into slices.
Turn to your right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator on the shelf above the drawers.
Turn around and walk back to the table, stopping beside the black chair.
Pick up a slice of potato that was previously cut.
Turn around and walk across the room, to the microwave that is on the counter top.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, heat the potato slice, then take the potato slice out of the microwave.
Turn to your left, facing the coffee pot.
Place the potato slice on the counter, in front of the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice on the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
